title: Dizzy Gillespie - Gillespiana + Live Quintet Version (1960) PWR
description:
DIZZY GILLESPIE - GILLESPIANA

Dizzy Gillespie, Clark Terry, Ernie Royal, Joe Wilder, John Frosk (tp), Paul Faulise (b-tb), Julius Watkins, Gunther Schuller, Jimmy Buffington, Al Richman (fhr), Don Butterfield (tu), Leo Wright (as, fl), Lalo Schifrin (p, comp), Art Davis (b), Chuck Lampkin (d), Candido Camero (cga), Jack Del Rio (bgo), Willie Rodriguez (timb), Morris Scott, William Lester (fhr) replace Buffington & Richman on 5.
New York, November 14-16, 1960

01. Prelude    [5:56]
02. Blues    [11:20]
03. Panamericana    [4:42]

05. Toccata    [12:03]

Salle Pleyel, Paris, France, November 25, 1960

07. Blues (live quintet version)    [10:55]

The first 5 tracks were origanally released as Gillespiana on Verve or Clef or whatever. I don't know from where the live tracks (they couldn't fit one of them) were culled
